msgctxt "ee569fe8-e141-4fb2-aeea-d41b28904d06"
msgid ""
"The terrible curse the Lantern King bestowed upon you, tying you and your "
"companions to your kingdom's current state. As your kingdom crumbles, you "
"wither and die.\n"
